\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2019/04/190411_sonyx1c_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2019%2F04%2F190411_sonyx1c_02.jpg&h=47083b43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n現在日本的電訊商已宣佈夏季手機的推出名單，當中有 Sony Xperia 1，但就沒有 Sony Xperia 1 Compact。看來 Sony Xperia 1 Compact 最快要到秋季才會面世。"},{"pid":"f618d0814aa2ee5359744825185f31cbe4bc5ebc","tid":1191754,"uid":41298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d8d608c40859aee0be3be01ad2946ac447f1eff","tid":1191754,"uid":3704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ded7b02cf7a1020a2a27fb5eebbcb89c9a1ab2b5","tid":1191754,"uid":41298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d27a533fd4fa62ccc533cae076715262710c69b8","tid":1191754,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"換個新名重新出發<br />\n4月新財年果陣D部門重組左<br />\n所以宜家部1仔先有相機部門同電視部門幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"上綱搵到呢條拎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/gadgets.ndtv.com/sony-xperia-2-12991%3famp=1&amp;akamai-rum=off\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fgadgets.ndtv.com%2Fsony-xperia-2-12991%253famp%3D1%26akamai-rum%3Doff&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=8677cb0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/gadgets.ndtv.com/sony-xperia-2-12991%3famp=1&amp;akamai-rum=off</a><br />\n<br />\nSony Xperia 2 is an upcoming smartphone by Sony. The phone is rumoured to come with a 6.20-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1234x2880 pixels and an aspect ratio of 21:9.<br />\n<br />\n即係sony從此無細機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打賜教，我仲未接受到要搵第間廠嘅細機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-